# Production launch checklist:
# - set SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=prod
# - replace POSTGRES_PASSWORD with at least 12 non-placeholder characters
# - replace ZEROON_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET with at least 32 random characters
# - replace ZEROON_LOCAL_VERIFICATION_CODE until Sprint 08 production SMS work removes it
